                 gets index of matching pathspec entry); can be NULL;
                 return 0 to add, >0 to skip, 
<
0 to abort scan.

notification callback for each updated path (also
                 gets index of matching pathspec entry); can be NULL;
                 return 0 to add, >0 to skip, 
